quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  9,1,( ae ahal islam ab ) khuda aur is ke rasool ki taraf se mushrikon se jin se tum ne ehad kar rakha tha bezari ( aur jung ki tayari ) hai
  9,2,to ( mushrako tum ) zameen mein chaar mahinay chal phir lau aur jaan rakho ke tum khuda ko aajiz nah krsko ge. aur yeh bhi ke khuda kafiroon ko ruswa karne wala hai
  9,3,aur hajj akbar ke din khuda aur is ke rasool ki taraf se logon ko aagah kiya jata hai ke khuda mushrikon se bezaar hai aur is ka rasool bhi ( un se dastbrdar hai ). pas agar tum tauba karlo to tumhare haq mein behtar hai. aur agar nah manu ( aur khuda se muqaabla karo ) to jaan rakho ke tum khuda ko hara nahi sakuu ge aur ( ae paighambar ) kafiroon ko dukh dainay walay azaab ki khabar suna do
  9,4,Albata jin mushrikon ke sath tum ne ehadkiya ho aur unhon ne tumhara kisi terhan ka qasoor nahkiya ho aur nah tumahray muqablay mein kisi ki madad ki ho to jis muddat taq un ke sath ehadkiya ho usay poora karo. ( ke ) khuda parhaiz garon ko dost rakhta hai
  9,5,jab izzat ke mahinay guzar jayen to mushrikon ko jahan pao qatal kar do aur pakarlo aur ghair lo aur har ghaat ki jagah un ki taak mein baithy raho. phir agar woh tauba karlen aur namaz parhnay aur zakaat dainay lagen to un ki raah chore do. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  9,6,aur agar koi mushriq tum se panah ka khawastgah ho to is ko panah do yahan taq ke kalaam khuda suneney lagey phir is ko aman ki jagah wapas pohncha do. is liye ke yeh be khabar log hain
  9,7,bhala mushrikon ke liye ( jinhon ne ehad toar dala ) khuda aur is ke rasool ke nazdeek ehad kionkar ( qaim ) reh sakta hai haan jin logon ke sath tum ne masjid mohtaram ( yani khanah kaaba ) ke nazdeek ehadkiya hai agar woh ( apne ehad par ) qaim rahen to tum bhi apne qoul وقرار ( par ) qaim raho. be shak khuda parhaiz gaaron ko dost rakhta hai
  9,8,( bhala un se ehad ) kionkar ( poorakiya jaye jab un ka yeh haal hai ) ke agar tum par ghalba paleen to nah qaraabat ka lehaaz karen nah ehad ka. yeh munh se to tumhe khush kar dete hain lekin un ke dil ( un baton ko ) qubool nahi karte. aur un mein aksar nafarman hain
  9,9,yeh khuda ki ayaton ke aiwz thora sa faida haasil karte aur logon ko khuda ke raste se roktay hain. kuch shak nahi ke jo kaam yeh karte hain buray hain
  9,10,yeh log kisi momin ke haq mein nah to rishta daari ka paas karte hain nah ehad ka. aur yeh hadd se tajawaz karne walay hain
  9,11,agar yeh tauba karlen aur namaz parhnay aur zakaat dainay lagen to deen mein tumahray bhai hain. aur samajhney walay logon ke liye hum apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan karte hain
  9,12,aur agar ehad karne ke baad apni qasmon ko toar dalain aur tumahray deen mein taanay karne lagen to un kufar ke pishwaon se jung karo ( yeh yeh be imaan log hain aur ) un ki qasmon ka kuch aitbaar nahi hai. ajab nahi ke ( apni harkaat se ) baz ajayeen
  9,13,bhala tum aisay logon se kyun nah laro jinhon ne apni qasmon ko toar dala aur paighambar ( khuda ) ke jala watan karne ka azm musammam kar liya aur unhon ne tum se ( ehad shikni ki ) ibtida ki.kiya tum aisay logon se drtay ho halaank darny ke Laiq khuda hai bashart e kay imaan rakhtay ho
  9,14,un se ( khoob ) laro. khuda un ko tumahray hathon se azaab mein daaley ga aur ruswa kere ga aur tum ko un par ghalba day ga aur momin logon ke seenon ko Shifa bakhshay ga
  9,15,aur un ke dilon se gussa daur kere ga aur jis par chahay ga rehmat kere ga. aur khuda sab kuch jaanta ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,16,kiya tum log yeh khayaal karte ho ke ( be azmaish ) chore diye jao ge aur abhi khuda ne aisay logon ko mutamayyaz kiya hi nahi jinhon ne tum mein se jehaad kiye aur khuda aur is ke rasool aur mominon ke siwa kisi ko dili dost nahi banaya. aur khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  9,17,mushrikon ki zaiba nahi ke khuda ki masjidoon ko abad karen jab ke woh apne aap par kufar ki gawahi day rahay hain. un logon ke sab aamaal be car hain aur yeh hamesha dozakh mein rahen ge
  9,18,khuda ki masjidoon ko to woh log abad karte hain jo khuda par aur roz qayamat par imaan laatay hain aur namaz parhte aur زکواة dete hain aur khuda ke siwa kisi se nahi drtay. yahi log umeed hai ke hadaayat Yafta logon mein ( daakhil ) hon
  9,19,kiya tum ne hajion ko pani pilana aur masjid mohtaram yani ( Khana kaaba ) ko abad karna is shakhs ke aamaal jaissa khayaalkiya hai jo khuda aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhta hai aur khuda ki raah mein jehaad karta hai. yeh log khuda ke nazdeek barabar nahi hain. aur khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  9,20,jo log imaan laaye aur watan chore gay aur khuda ki raah mein maal aur jaan se jehaad karte rahay. khuda ke haan un ke darjay bohat barray hain. aur wohi morad ko pounchanay walay hain
  9,21,un ka perwar-digaar un ko apni rehmat ki aur khushnodi ki aur bahishtoon ki khushkhabri deta hai jin mein un ke liye Nemat haae javedani hai
  9,22,( aur woh ) un mein abdul aabad rahen ge. kuch shak nahi ke khuda ke haan bara sila ( tayyar ) hai
  9,23,ae ahal imaan! agar tumahray ( maa ) baap aur ( behan ) bhai imaan ke maqabil kufar ko pasand karen to un se dosti nah rakho. aur jo un se dosti rakhen ge woh zalim hain
  9,24,keh do ke agar tumahray baap aur betay aur bhai aur aurtain aur khandan ke aadmi aur maal jo tum kamate ho aur tijarat jis ke band honay se drtay ho aur makanaat jin ko pasand karte ho khuda aur is ke rasool se aur khuda ki raah mein jehaad karne se tumhe ziyada Aziz hon to thehray raho yahan taq ke khuda apna hukum ( yani azaab ) beje. aur khuda nafarman logon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  9,25,khuda ne bohat se moqaon par tum ko madad di hai aur ( jung ) Hunain ke din. jab tum ko apni ( jamaat ki ) kasrat par ghara tha to woh tumahray kuch bhi kaam nah aayi. aur zameen bawajood ( itni barri ) farakhi ke tum par tang hogayi phir tum peeth phair kar phir gay
  9,26,phir khuda ne apne paighambar par aur mominon par apni taraf se taskeen nazil farmai ( aur tumhari madad ko firshton ke ) lashkar jo tumhe nazar nahi atay they ( aasman se ) utaray aur kafiroon ko azaab diya. aur kufar karne walon ki yahi saza hai
  9,27,phir khuda is ke baad jis par chahay meharbani se tavajja farmaiye aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  9,28,momino! mushriq to palidh hain to is baras ke baad woh Khana kaaba ka paas nah jaane payen aur agar tum ko muflisi ka khauf ho to khuda chahay ga to tum ko apne fazl se ghanni kar day ga. be shak khuda sab kuch jaanta ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,29,jo ahal kitaab mein se khuda par imaan nahi laatay aur nah roz akhirat par ( yaqeen rakhtay hain ) aur nah un cheezon ko haraam samajte hain jo khuda aur is ke rasool ne haraam ki hain aur nah deen haq ko qubool karte hain un se jung karo yahan taq ke zaleel hokar apne haath se jaziya den
  9,30,aur yahood kehte hain ke uzair khuda ke betay hain aur isaai kehte hain ke maseeh khuda ke betay hain. yeh un ke munh ki baatein hain pehlay kafir bhi isi terhan ki baatein kaha karte they yeh bhi inhen ki race karne mein lagey hain. khuda un ko halaak kere. yeh kahan behke phirtay hain
  9,31,unhon ne apne ulama aur mashaiykh aur maseeh Ibn maryam ko allah ke siwa khuda bana liya halaank unn ko yeh hukum diya gaya tha ke khuday-e wahid ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karen. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. aur woh un logon ke shareek muqarrar karne se pak hai
  9,32,yeh chahtay hain ke khuda ke noor ko apne munh se ( phoonk maar kar ) bujha den aur khuda apne noor ko poora kiye baghair rehne ka nahi. agarchay kafiroon ko bura hi lagey
  9,33,wohi to hai jis ne apne paighambar ko hadaayat aur deen haq day kar bheja taakay is ( deen ) ko ( duniya ke ) tamam deeno par ghalib kere. agarchay kafir nakhush hi hon
  9,34,momino! ( ahal kitaab ke ) bohat se aalam aur mashaiykh logon ka maal na-haq khatay aur ( un ko ) raah khuda se roktay hain. aur jo log sona aur chandi jama karte hain aur is ko khuda ke raste mein kharch nahi karte. un ko is din azaab alim ki khabar suna do
  9,35,jis din woh maal dozakh ki aag mein ( khoob ) garamkiya jaye ga. phir is se un ( bakhilon) ki pishanyan aur pehlu aur pithain daghi jayen gi ( aur kaha jaye ga ) ke yeh wohi hai jo tum ne apne liye jamakiya tha so jo tum jama karte they ( ab ) is ka maza chako
  9,36,khuda ke nazdeek mahinay ginti mein ( baara hain yani ) is roz ( se ) ke is ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya. kitaab khuda mein ( baras ke ) baara mahinay ( likhay hue ) hain. un mein se chaar mahinay adab ke hain. yahi deen ( ka ) seedha rasta hai. to un ( mahino ) mein ( qtal na-haq se ) apne aap par zulm nah karna. aur tum sab ke sab mushrikon se laro jaisay woh sab ke sab tum se lartay hain. aur jaan rakho ke khuda parhaiz gaaron ke sath hai
  9,37,aman ke kis mahinay ko hata kar agay peechay kar dena kufar mein izafah karta hai is se kafir gumraahi mein parre rehtay hain. aik saal to is ko halal samajh letay hain aur dosray saal haraam. taakay adab ke mahino ko jo khuda ne muqarrar kiye hain ginti poori kar len. aur jo khuda ne manakiya hai is ko jaaiz kar len. un ke buray aamaal un ke bhallay dikhayi dete hain. aur khuda kafir logon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  9,38,momino! tumhekiya howa hai ke jab tum se kaha jata hai ke khuda ki raah mein ( jehaad ke liye ) niklo to tum ( kahili ke sabab se ) zameen par giray jatay ho ( yani gharon se niklana nahi chahtay )kiya tum akhirat ( ki nematon ) ko chore kar dena ki zindagi par khush ho baithy ho. duniya ki zindagi ke faiday to akhirat ke maqabil bohat hi kam hain
  9,39,aur agar tum nah niklo ge to khuda tum ko barri takleef ka azaab day ga. aur tumhari jagah aur log peda kar day ga ( jo khuda ke poooray farmanbardar hon ge ) aur tum is ko kuch nuqsaan nah pouncha sakuu ge aur khuda har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  9,40,agar tum paighambar ki madad nah karo ge to khuda unn ka madadgaar hai ( woh waqt tum ko yaad hoga ) jab un ko kafiroon ne ghar se nikaal diya. ( is waqt ) do ( hi aisay shakhs they jin ) mein ( aik abubaker they ) aur dosray ( khud rasool allah ) jab woh dono ghaar ( Sore ) mein they is waqt paighambar apne Rafeeq ko tasalii dete they ke gham nah karo khuda hamaray sath hai. to khuda ne un par taskeen nazil farmai aur un ko aisay lashkaron se madad di jo tum ko nazar nahi atay they aur kafiroon ki baat ko pust kar diya. aur baat to khuda hi ki buland hai. aur khuda zabardast ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,41,"tum subak-baar ho ya giran-baar ( yani maal o asbaab thora rakhtay ho ya bohat, gharon se ) nikal aao. aur khuda ke raste mein maal aur jaan se laro. yahi tumahray haq mein acha hai bashart e kay samjhoo"
  9,42,agar mal-e ghanemat sahal al husool aur safar bhi halka sa hota to tumahray sath ( shoq se ) chal dete. lekin masafat un ko daur ( daraaz ) nazar aayi ( to izr karen ge ). aur khuda ki kasmain khayen ge ke agar hum taaqat rakhtay to aap ke sath zaroor nikal kharray hotay yeh ( aisay uzron se ) apne tain halaak kar rahay hain. aur khuda jaanta hai ke jhutay hain
  9,43,khuda tumhe maaf kere. tum ne peshtar is ke ke tum par woh log bhi zahir ho jatay hain jo sachey hain aur woh bhi tumhe maloom ho jatay jo jhutay hain unn ko ijazat kyun di
  9,44,jo log khuda par aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain woh to tum se ijazat nahi mangte ( ke peechay reh jayen balkay chahtay hain ke ) apne maal aur jaan se jehaad karen. aur khuda darny walon se waaqif hai
  9,45,ijazat wohi log mangte hain jo khuda par aur pichlle din par imaan nahi rakhtay aur un ke dil shak mein parre hue hain. so woh apne shak mein danwaan doll ho rahay hain
  9,46,aur agar woh niklny ka iradah karte hain to is ke liye samaan tayyar karte lekin khuda ne un ka uthna ( aur niklana ) pasand nahkiya to un ko hilnay julne hi nah diya aur ( un se ) keh diya gaya ke jahan ( mazoor ) baithy hain tum bhi un ke sath baithy raho
  9,47,agar woh tum mein ( shaamil hokar ) nikal bhi kharray hotay to tumahray haq mein shararat karte aur tum mein fasaad dalwanay ki gharz se doray doray phirtay aur tum mein un ke jasoos bhi hain aur khuda zaalmon ko khoob jaanta hai
  9,48,yeh pehlay bhi taalib fasaad rahay hain aur bohat si baton mein tumahray liye ulat phair karte rahay hain. yahan taq ke haq aap_hncha aur khuda ka hukum ghalib howa aur woh bura mantay hi reh gay
  9,49,aur un mein koi aisa bhi hai jo kehta hai ke mujhe to ijazat hi dijiye aur aafat mein nah dalye. dekho yeh aafat mein prhgye hain aur dozakh sab kafiroon ko ghairay hue hai
  9,50,( ae paighambar ) agar tum ko asayish haasil hoti hai to un ko buri lagti hai. aur koi mushkil padtee hai to kehte ke hum ne apna kaam pehlay hain ( durust ) kar liya tha aur khusihyan manate lout jatay hain
  9,51,keh do ke hum ko koi museebat nahi poanch sakti bajuz is ke jo khuda ne hamaray liye likh di ho wohi hamara karsaaz hai. aur mominon ko khuda hi ka bharosa rakhna chahiye
  9,52,keh do ke tum hamaray haq mein do bhulaiyon mein se aik ke munhtazir ho aur hum tumahray haq mein is baat ke munhtazir hain ke khuda ( ya to ) apne paas se tum par koi azaab nazil kere ya hamaray hathon se ( azaab dlwaye ) to tum bhi intzaar karo hum bhi tumahray sath intzaar karte hain
  9,53,keh do ke tum ( maal ) khusi se kharch karo ya na khushi se tum se hargiz qubool nahikiya jaye ga tum nafarman log ho
  9,54,aur un ke kharch ( mwal ) ke qubool honay se koi cheez Maney nahi hui siwa is ke unhon ne khuda se aur is ke rasool se kufarkiya aur namaz ko atay hain to sust kaahil hokar aur kharch karte hain to na khushi se
  9,55,tum un ke maal aur aulaad se taajjub nah karna. khuda chahta hai ke un cheezon se duniya ki zindagi mein un ko azaab day aur ( jab ) un ki jaan niklay to ( is waqt bhi ) woh kafir hi hon
  9,56,aur khuda ki kasmain khatay hain ke woh tum hi mein se hain halaank ho tum mein se nahi hain. asal yeh hai ke yeh darpook log hain
  9,57,agar un ki koi bachao ki jagah ( jaisay qilah ) ya ghaar o mughaak ya ( zameen ke andar ) ghusnay ki jagah mil jaye to isi taraf rasiyaan turatay hu-ay bhaag jayen
  9,58,aur un mein se baaz usay bhi hain ke ( taqseem ) sadqat mein tum par tana zani karte hain. agar un ko is mein se ( khatir khuwa ) mil jaye to khush rahen aur agar ( is qader ) nah miley to jhat khafa ho jayen
  9,59,aur agar woh is par khush rehtay jo khuda aur is ke rasool ne un ko diya tha. aur kehte ke hamein khuda kaafi hai aur khuda apne fazl se aur is ke paighambar ( apni meharbani se ) hamein ( phir ) den ge. aur hamein to khuda hi ki khwahish hai ( to un ke haq mein behtar hota )
  9,60,sadqat ( yani zakaat wa kherat ) to mflson aur mohtajon aur karkunaan sadqat ka haq hai aur un logon ka jin ki taleef qaloob Manzoor hai aur ghulamoo ke azad karanay mein aur qarzdaron ( ke qarz ada karne mein ) aur khuda ki raah mein aur musafiron ( ki madad ) mein ( bhi yeh maal kharch karna chahiye yeh haqooq ) khuda ki taraf se muqarrar kar diye gay hain aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,61,aur un mein baaz aisay hain jo paighambar ko aeza dete hain aur kehte hain ke yeh shakhs nira kaan hai. ( un se ) keh do ke ( woh ) kaan ( hai to ) tumhari bhalai ke liye. woh khuda ka aur mominon ( ki baat ) ka yaqeen rakhta hai aur jo log tum mein se imaan laaye hain un ke liye rehmat hai. aur jo log rasool khuda ko ranj pohanchate hain un ke liye azaab alim ( tayyar ) hai
  9,62,momino! yeh log tumahray samnay khuda ki kasmain khatay hain taakay tum ko khush kar den. halaank agar yeh ( dil se ) momin hotay to khuda aur is ke paighambar khush karne ke ziyada mustahiq hain
  9,63,kiya un logon ko maloom nahi ke jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool se muqaabla karta hai to is ke liye jahannum ki aag ( tayyar ) hai jis mein woh hamesha ( jalta ) rahay ga. yeh barri ruswai hai
  9,64,munhafiq drtay rehtay hain ke un ( ke paighambar ) par kahin koi aisi sourat ( nah ) utar aeye ke un ke dil ki baton ko un ( musalmanoon ) par zahir kar day. keh do ke hansi kiye jao. jis baat se tum drtay ho khuda is ko zaroor zahir kardey ga
  9,65,aur agar tum un se ( is baray mein ) daryaft karo to kahin ge hum to yun hi baat cheet aur dil lagi karte they. kahokiya tum khuda aur is ki ayaton aur is ke rasool se hansi karte they
  9,66,bahanay mat banaao tum imaan laane ke baad kafir ho chuke ho. agar hum tum mein se aik jamaat ko maaf kar dein to doosri jamaat ko saza bhi den ge kyunkay woh gunah karte rahay hain
  9,67,munhafiq mard aur munhafiq aurtain aik dosray ke hum jins ( yani aik terhan ke ) hain ke buray kaam karne ko kehte aur naik kamon se mana karte aur ( kharch karne se ) haath band kiye rehtay hain. unhon ne khuda ko bhala diya to khuda ne un ko bhala diya. be shak munhafiq nafarman hain
  9,68,allah ne munhafiq mardon aur munhafiq aurton aur kafiroon se aatish jahannum ka wadakiya hai jis mein hamesha ( jaltay ) rahen ge. wohi un ke Laiq hai. aur khuda ne un par laanat kar di hai. aur un ke liye hamesha ka azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  9,69,"( tum munhafiq log ) un logon ki terhan ho, jo tum se pehlay ho chukay hain. woh tum se bohat ziyada taaqatwar aur maal o aulaad mein kahin ziyada they to woh apne hissay se behra yab ho chukay. so jis terhan tum se pehlay log apne hissay se faida utha chuke hain. isi terhan tum ne apne hissay se faida utha liya. aur jis terhan woh baatil mein doobe rahay isi terhan tum baatil mein doobe rahay yeh woh log hain jin ke aamaal duniya aur akhirat mein zaya hogaye. aur yahi nuqsaan uthany walay hain"
  9,70,kiya un ko un logon ( ke halaat ) ki khabar nahi pohanchi jo un se pehlay they ( yani ) Nooh aur Aad aur smod ki qoum. aur ibrahim ki qoum aur Mudin walay aur ulti hui bustiyon walay. un ke paas paighambar nishanain le le kar aeye. aur khuda to aisa nah tha ke un par zulm karta lekin wohi apne aap par zulm karte they
  9,71,aur momin mard aur momin aurtain aik dosray ke dost hain ke achay kaam karne ko kehte hain aur buri baton se mana karte aur namaz parhte aur zakaat dete aur khuda aur is ke rasool ki itaat karte hain. yahi log hain jin par khuda reham kere ga. be shak khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  9,72,khuda ne momin mardon aur momin aurton se bahishtoon ka wadakiya hai jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain ( woh ) un mein hamesha rahen ge aur bahisht haae javedani mein nafees makanaat ka ( wadakiya hai ) aur khuda ki Raza mandi to sab se barh kar Nemat hai yahi barri kamyabi hai
  9,73,ae paighambar! kafiroon aur munhafiqon se laro. aur un par sakhti karo. aur un ka thikana دورخ hai aur woh buri jagah hai
  9,74,yeh khuda ki kasmain khatay hain ke unhon ne ( to kuch ) nahi kaha halaank unhon ne kufar ka kalma kaha hai aur yeh islam laane ke baad kafir hogaye hain aur aisi baat ka qasad kar chukay hain jis par qudrat nahi paske. aur unhon ne ( musalmanoon mein ) aib hi kon sa dekha hai siwa is ke ke khuda ne apne fazl se aur is ke paighambar ne ( apni meharbani se ) un ko doulat mand kar diya hai. to agar yeh log tauba karlen to un ke haq mein behtar hoga. aur agar munh phair len to un ko duniya aur akhirat mein dukh dainay wala azaab day ga aur zameen mein un ka koi dost aur madadgaar nah hoga
  9,75,aur un mein se baaz aisay hain jinhon ne khuda se ehadkiya tha ke agar woh hum ko apni meharbani se ( maal ) ataa farmaiye ga to hum zaroor khairaatkiya karen ge aur naik karon mein ho jayen ge
  9,76,lekin jab khuda ne un ko apne fazl se ( maal ) diya to is mein bukhal karne lagey aur ( apne ehad se ) rogrdani karkay phir baithy
  9,77,to khuda ne is ka injaam yehkiya ke is roz taq ke liye jis mein woh khuda ke rubaroo haazir hon ge un ke dilon mein nifaq daal diya is liye ke unhon ne khuda se jo wadakiya tha is ke khilaafkiya aur is liye ke woh jhoot boltay they
  9,78,kiya un ko maloom nahi ke khuda un ke bheidoon aur mashwaron taq se waaqif hai aur yeh ke woh ghaib ki baatein jan-nay wala hai
  9,79,jo ( Zee istetat ) musalman dil khol kar khairaat karte hain aur jo ( be chaaray ghareeb sirf itna hi kama satke hain jitni mazdoori karte ( aur thori si kamaai mein se kharch bhi karte ) hain un par jo ( munhafiq ) ta'an karte hain aur hanstay hain. khuda un par hanstaa hai aur un ke liye takleef dainay wala azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  9,80,tum un ke liye bakhshish mango ya nah mango. ( baat aik hai ). agar un ke liye sattar dafaa bhi bakhshish mango ge to bhi khuda un ko nahi bakhshay ga. yeh is liye ke unhon ne khuda aur is ke rasool se kufarkiya. aur khuda nafarman logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  9,81,jo log ( غزوہٴ tabook mein ) peechay reh gay woh paighambar khuda ( ki marzi ) ke khilaaf baithy rehne se khush hue aur is baat ko napasandkiya ke khuda ki raah mein apne maal aur jaan se jehaad karen. aur ( ouron se bhi ) kehnay lagey ke garmi mein mat niklana. ( un se ) keh do ke dozakh ki aag is se kahin ziyada garam hai. kash yeh ( is baat ) ko samajte
  9,82,yeh ( duniya mein ) thora sa hans len aur ( akhirat mein ) un ko un aamaal ke badlay jo karte rahay hain bohat sa rona hoga
  9,83,phir agar khuda tum ko un mein se kisi giroh ki taraf le jaye aur woh tum se niklny ki ijazat talab karen to keh dena ke tum mere sath hargiz nahi niklo ge aur nah mere sath ( madadgaar hokar ) dushman se larai karo ge. tum pehli dafaa baith rehne se khush hue to ab bhi peechay rehne walon ke sath baithy raho
  9,84,aur ( ae paighambar ) un mein se koi mar jaye to kabhi is ( ke janazay ) par namaz nah parhna aur nah is ki qabar par ( ja kar ) kharray hona. yeh khuda aur is ke rasool ke sath kufar karte rahay aur marey bhi nafarman ( hi marey )
  9,85,un ke aulaad aur maal se taajjub nah karna. un cheezon se khuda yeh chahta hai ke un ko duniya mein azaab kere aur ( jab ) un ki jaan niklay to ( is waqt bhi ) yeh kafir hi hon
  9,86,aur jab koi sourat nazil hoti hai ke khuda par imaan lao aur is ke rasool ke sath ho kar larai karo to jo un mein doulat mand hain woh tum se ijazat talab karte hain aur kehte hain ke hamein to rehne hi dijiye ke jo log gharon mein rahen ge hum bhi un ke sath rahen
  9,87,yeh is baat se khush hain ke aurton ke sath jo peechay reh jati hain. ( gharon mein baith ) rahen un ke dilon par mohar laga di gayi hai to yeh samajte hi nahi
  9,88,lekin paighambar aur jo log un ke sath imaan laaye sab apne maal aur jaan se larray. inhen logon ke liye bhalaiyan hain. aur yahi morad panay walay hain
  9,89,khuda ne un ke liye baagaat tayyar kar rakhay hain jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain hamesha un mein rahi ge. yeh barri kamyabi hai
  9,90,aur sehraa nasheenon mein se bhi kuch log izr karte hue ( tumahray paas ) aeye ke un ko bhi ijazat di jaye aur jinhon ne khuda aur is ke rasool se jhoot bola woh ( ghar mein ) baith rahay so jo log un mein se kafir hue hain un ko dukh dainay wala azaab puhanche ga
  9,91,nah to zaeefon par kuch gunah hai aur nah bimaroon par nah un par jin ke paas kharch mojood nahi ( ke shareek jehaad nah hon yani ) jab ke khuda aur is ke rasool ke Khairandesh ( aur dil se un ke sath ) hon. naiko karon par kisi terhan ka ilzaam nahi hai. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  9,92,"aur nah un ( be srosaman ) logon par ( ilzaam ) hai ke tumahray paas aeye ke un ko sawari do aur tum ne kaha ke mere paas koi aisi cheez nahi jis par tum ko sawaar karoon to woh lout gay aur is gham se ke un ke paas kharch mojood nah tha, un ki aankhon se ansoo beh rahay they"
  9,93,ilzaam to un logon par hai. jo doulat mand hain aur ( phir ) tum se ijazat talab karte hain ( yani ) is baat se khush hain ke aurton ke sath jo peechay reh jati hain ( gharon mein baith ) rahen. khuda ne un ke dilon par mohar kar di hai pas woh samajte hi nahi
  9,94,jab tum un ke paas wapas jao ge to tum se izr karen ge tum kehna ke mat izr karo hum hargiz tumhari baat nahi manen ge khuda ne hum ko tumahray sab halaat bta diye hain. aur abhi khuda aur is ka rasool tumahray amlon ko ( aur ) dekhen ge phir tum gayab o hazir ke jan-nay walay ( khuday-e wahid ) ki taraf lout’tay jao ge aur jo amal tum karte rahay ho woh sab tumhe betaye ga
  9,95,jab tum un ke paas lout kar jao ge to tumahray rubaroo khuda ki kasmain khayen ge taakay tum un se dar guzar karo so unn ki taraf iltifaat nah karna. yeh napak hain aur jo yeh kaam karte rahay hain is ke badla un ka thikana dozakh hai
  9,96,yeh tumahray agay kasmain khayen ge taakay tum un se khush ho jao lekin agar tum unn se khush ho jao ge to khuda to nafarman logon se khush nahi hota
  9,97,dehati log sakht kafir aur sakht munhafiq hain aur is qabil hain ke jo ehkaam ( Shariat ) khuda ne apne rasool par nazil farmaiye hain un se waaqif ( hi ) nah hon. aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,98,aur baaz dehati aisay hain ke jo kharch karte hain usay tawwan samajte hain aur tumahray haq mein musibaton ke munhtazir hain. un hi par buri museebat ( waqay ) ho. aur khuda suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  9,99,aur baaz dehati aisay hain ke khuda par aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain aur jo kuch kharch karte hain is ko khuda ki Qurbat aur paighambar ki duaon ka zareya samajte hain. dekho woh be shuba un ke liye ( mojab ) qurbat hai khuda un ko anqareeb apni rehmat mein daakhil kere ga. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  9,100,jin logon ne Sabqat ki ( yani sab se ) pehlay ( imaan laaye ) muhajreen mein se bhi aur Ansar mein se bhi. aur jinhon ne naiko kaari ke sath un ki pairwi ki khuda un se khush hai aur woh khuda se khush hain aur is ne un ke liye baagaat tayyar kiye hain jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain aur hamesha un mein rahen ge. yeh barri kamyabi hai
  9,101,aur tumahray gird o nawah ke baaz dehati munhafiq hain aur baaz madeeney walay bhi nifaq par uray hue hain tum inhen nahi jantay. hum jantay hain. hum un ko dohra azaab den ge phir woh barray azaab ki taraf lout’tay jayen ge
  9,102,aur kuch aur log hain ke apne gunaaho ka ( saaf ) iqraar karte hain unhon ne achay buray amlon ko mila jala diya tha. qareeb hai ke khuda un par meharbani se tavajja farmaiye. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  9,103,un ke maal mein se zakaat qubool kar lau ke is se tum un ko ( zahir mein bhi ) pak aur ( batin mein bhi ) pakeeza karte ho aur un ke haq mein duaye kher karo ke tumhari dua un ke liye mojab taskeen hai aur khuda suneney wala aur jan-nay wala hai
  9,104,kiya yeh log nahi jantay ke khuda hi apne bundon se tauba qubool farmata hai aur sadqat ( wa kherat ) laita hai aur be shak khuda hi tauba qubool karne wala meharban hai
  9,105,aur un se keh do ke amal kiye jao. khuda aur is ka rasool aur momin ( sab ) tumahray amlon ko dekh len ge. aur tum gayab o hazir ke jan-nay walay ( khuday-e wahid ) ki taraf lout’tay jao ge phir jo kuch tum karte rahay ho woh sab tum ko bta day ga
  9,106,aur kuch aur log hain jin ka kaam khuda ke hukum par moqoof hai. chahay un ko azaab day aur chahay un ko maaf kar day. aur khuda jan-nay wala aur hikmat wala hai
  9,107,aur ( un mein se aisay bhi hain ) jinhon ne is gharz se masjid banwai ke zarrar puhanchayen aur kufar karen aur mominon mein tafarruqa dalain aur jo log khuda aur is ke rasool se pehlay jung kar chukay hain un ke liye ghaat ki jagah banayen. aur kasmain khayen ge ke hamara maqsood to sirf bhalai thi. magar khuda gawahi deta hai ke yeh jhutay hain
  9,108,tum is ( masjid ) mein kabhi ( jaakar ) kharray bhi nah hona. Albata woh masjid jis ki bunyaad pehlay din se taqwa par rakhi gayi hai is qabil hai ke is mein jaya ( aur namaz parhaya ) karo. is mein aisay log hain jo ke pak rehne ko pasand karte hain. aur khuda pak rehne walon ko hi pasand karta hai
  9,109,bhala jis shakhs ne apni imarat ki bunyaad khuda ke khauf aur is ki razamandi par rakhi woh acha hai ya woh jis ne apni imarat ki bunyaad gir jaane wali khayi ke kinare par rakhi ke woh is ko dozakh ki aag mein le giri aur khuda zaalmon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  9,110,yeh imarat jo unhon ne banai hai hamesha un ke dilon mein ( mojab ) Khuljan rahay gi ( aur un ko mutaradad rakhay gi ) magar yeh ke un ke dil paash paash ho jayen aur khuda jan-nay wala aur hikmat wala hai
  9,111,khuda ne mominon se un ki jaanen aur un ke maal khareed liye hain ( aur is ke ) aiwz un ke liye bahisht ( tayyar ki ) hai. yeh log khuda ki raah mein lartay hain to maartay bhi hain aur maaray bhi jatay hain bhi hain. yeh torat aur injeel aur quran mein sacha wada hai. jis ka poora karna usay zaroor hai aur khuda se ziyada wada poora karne wala kon hai to jo soda tum ne is sekiya hai is se khush raho. aur yahi barri kamyabi hai
  9,112,"tauba karne walay, ibadat karne walay, hamd karne walay, roza rakhnay walay, ruku karne walay, sajda karne walay, naik kamon ka amar karne walay, buri baton se mana karne walay, khuda ki hado ki hifazat karne walay, ( yahi momin log hain ) aur ae paighambar mominon ko ( bahisht ki ) khush khaberi suna do"
  9,113,paighambar aur musalmanoon ko Shayaan nahi ke jab un par zahir hogaya ke mushriq ahal dozakh hain. to un ke liye bakhshish mangeen go woh un ke qaraabat daar hi hon
  9,114,aur ibrahim ka apne baap ke liye bakhshish maangna to aik waday ka sabab tha jo woh is se kar chuke they. lekin jab un ko maloom hogaya ke woh khuda ka dushman hai to is se bezaar hogaye. kuch shak nahi ke ibrahim barray naram dil aur muthammil they
  9,115,aur khuda aisa nahi ke kisi qoum ko hadaayat dainay ke baad gumraah kar day jab taq ke un ko woh cheez nah bta day jis se woh parhaiz karen. be shak khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  9,116,khuda hi hai jis ke liye asmano aur zamiinon ki badshahat hai. wohi zindagani bakhshta hai ( wohi ) mout deta hai aur khuda ke siwa tumhara koi dost aur madadgaar nahi hai
  9,117,be shak khuda ne paighambar par meharbani ki aur muhajreen aur Ansar par jo bawajood is ke ke un mein se bazon ke dil jald phir jaane ko they. mushkil ki gharri mein paighambar ke sath rahay. phir khuda ne un par meharbani farmai. be shak woh un par nihayat shafqat karne wala ( aur ) meharban hai
  9,118,aur un tenu par bhi jin ka maamla multawikiya gaya tha. yahan taq ke jab unhen zameen bawajood farakhi ke un par tang hogayi aur un ke jaanen bhi un par dobhr hogai. aur unhon ne jaan liya ke khuda ( ke haath ) se khud is ke siwa koi panah nahi. phir khuda ne un par meharbani ki taakay tauba karen. be shak khuda tauba qubool karne wala meharban hai
  9,119,ae ahal imaan! khuda se drtay raho aur raast bazoo ke sath raho
  9,120,"ahal madinah ko aur jo un ke aas paas dehati rehtay hain un ko Shayaan nah tha ke paighambar khuda se peechay reh jayen aur nah yeh ke apni jaanun ko un ki jaan se ziyada Aziz rakhen. yeh is liye ke inhen khuda ki raah mein takleef pahunchti hai pyaas ki, mehnat ki ya bhook ki ya woh aisi jagah chaltay hain ke kafiroon ko gussa aeye ya dushmanon se koi cheez letay hain to har baat par un ke liye amal naik likha jata hai. kuch shak nahi ke khuda naiko karon ka ajar zaya nahi karta"
  9,121,aur ( isi terhan ) jo woh kharch karte hain thora ya bohat ya koi maidan tey karte hain to yeh sab kuch un ke liye ( aamaal Saleha ) mein likh liya jata hai taakay khuda un ko un ke aamaal ka bohat acha badla day
  9,122,aur yeh to ho nahi sakta ke momin sab ke sab nikal ayen. to yun kyun nahkiya ke har aik jamaat mein se chand ashkhaas nikal jatay taakay deen ka ( ilm sikhte aur is ) mein samajh peda karte aur jab apni qoum ki taraf wapas atay to un ko dar sunaate taakay woh hizr(perhaiz) karte
  9,123,ae ehley imaan! apne nazdeek ke ( rehne walay ) kafiroon se jung karo aur chahiye ke woh tum mein sakhti ( yani mehnat o qowat jung ) maloom karen. aur jaan rakho ke khuda parhaiz gaaron ke sath hai
  9,124,aur jab koi sourat nazil hoti hai to baaz munhafiq (istehzaa karte aur ) puchhte ke is sourat ne tum mein se kis ka imaan ziyadakiya hai. so jo imaan walay hain un ka imaan to ziyadakiya aur woh khush hotay hain
  9,125,"aur jin ke dilon mein marz hai, un ke haq mein khbs par khbs ziyadakiya aur woh marey bhi to kafir ke kafir"
  9,126,kiya yeh dekhte nahi ke yeh har saal aik ya do baar bulaa mein phansa diye jatay hain phir bhi tauba nahi karte aur nah nasiyaat pakarte hain
  9,127,aur jab koi sourat nazil hoti hai aik dosray ki janib dekhnay lagtay hain ( aur puchhte hain ke ) bhala tumhe koi daikhta hai phir phir jatay hain. khuda ne un ke dilon ko phair rakha hai kyunkay yeh aisay log hain ke samajh se kaam nahi letay
  9,128,( logo ) tumahray paas tum hi mein se aik paighambar aeye hain. tumhari takleef un ko giran maloom hoti hai aur tumhari bhalai ke khwahish mand hain aur mominon par nihayat shafqat karne walay ( aur ) meharban hain
  9,129,phir agar yeh log phir jayen ( aur nah manen ) to keh do ke khuda mujhe kifayat karta hai is ke siwa koi mabood nahi isi par mera bharosa hai aur wohi arsh azeem ka maalik hai
